title: The Trout harvest
creator_credit: Ted Davis, Victoria. Dept. of Agriculture and Victoria. Dept. of Fisheries and Wildlife
brief_description: The Snobs Creek fish hatchery was newly established at this time, and this film shows how the fish are bred from the egg stage to liberation into rivers and lakes. This film was included in the San Francisco Film Festival 1961.
